Package: later
Type: Package
Title: A Periodic Batch Processing Framework 
Version: 0.1.2
Author: person("Ilias", "Kotinas", email = "henfiber@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Ilias Kotinas <henfiber@gmail.com>
Description: Utility functions for time-related modelling.
    Companion to the cronr package. This is a package that aids 
    in running analytical procedures in a periodic schedule. 
    It may be useful in batch processing pipelines where new data are made 
    available periodically
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), cronr, data.table
Imports: utils, lubridate, inline, parallel
Suggests: tcltk2, testthat
